I found a solution [here](https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-liquibase/issues/4). As suggested [in this post](https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-liquibase/issues/4#issuecomment-489592968), we can use the dependency (Gradle):
```
compile (&quot;org.liquibase:liquibase-core:3.6.3&quot;) {
    exclude group: &#39;org.springframework&#39;
}
```
which in my case translates to (Maven):
```
&lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;org.liquibase&lt;/groupId&gt;
	&lt;artifactId&gt;liquibase-core&lt;/artifactId&gt;
	&lt;version&gt;3.6.3&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
```
This solves the problem.

