```xml
&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;jakarta.platform&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;jakarta.jakartaee-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;10.0.0&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;
```

Or just the artifact causing the problem:

```xml
&lt;dependency&gt;
